  <hr style="border-top: 3px solid #e7e7e7;">

  <h2>Community of Care</h2>
  <p class="lead">
    Healthcare is a team sport. Great care often features coordination among a variety of health specialists or people, often including family. Why should you have to print out a copy of your medical records, which are bound to become out-of-date quickly, when you can simply connect people to your up-to-date record? 
  </p>
